  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Security] [Opponent's Turn] When an opponent's Digimon
    attacks, if all of your Digimon and Tamers have the [D-Reaper]\_trait, for each
    of 1 of your [Mother D-Reaper]'s digivolution cards, the attacking Digimon get
    -1000 DP for the turn.\n[Main] If you have no face-up security cards, by trashing
    your top security card, place this card face up as your top security card."
